{"tid":498308,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【修議規戰】立會否決中止待續議案 明早正式決戰修改議事規則","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T18:18:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60c19b0b324dc76af720d068bf2324195107621c","tid":498308,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57577646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57577646&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNsvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=5b43cdbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171213%2F57577646&h=41c3a742\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171213/57577646</a><br />\n<br />\n【修議規戰】立會否決中止待續議案 明早正式決戰修改議事規則<br />\n<br />\n3,849<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1213 20:21<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513167593_8b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513167593_8b6f.jpg&h=946bf074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公民黨楊岳橋就修改《議事規則》提出的中止待續議案，最終被否決。易仰民攝 (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513167812_507c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513167812_507c.jpg&h=af44449e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎樹雄攝 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171213/large/1513167814_ed1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171213%2Flarge%2F1513167814_ed1d.jpg&h=be3f10c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎樹雄攝 <br />\n<br />\n立法會在下午3時半開始恢復討論由公民黨楊岳橋就修改《議事規則》提出的中止待續議案，至晚上7時35分完成辯論，有關的議案最終在功能組別9票贊成、23票反對；地區直選13票贊成、16票反對下，議案被否決。立法會明早9時開始將會正式進入修改《議事規則》的討論，在主席梁君彥早已限制每名議員發言15分鐘，待所有議員發言後，修改《議事規則》的議案將進入表決。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋在總結發言時指，議員需要「停一停，諗一諗」，是否收緊呈請書制度，將提交呈請書即可成立專責委員會的門檻由20人提高至35人，而今早新民黨葉劉淑儀站立支持民主派提出的呈請書，證明呈請書有其作用，剎停修改《議事規則》亦有必要。他又指，建制派計劃降低全體委員會的法定人數有可能違憲，呼籲建制派需要再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n工黨張超雄在發言時指，不滿為求聖誕節前通過《議事規則》修改，要求延長會議至在下星期，影響4個事務委員會的運作，包括兒童權利小組委員會的公聽會，他指明年第一季公佈幼兒照顧服務長遠發展研究的檢討結果，看不到有在聖誕節前完成修改《議事規則》的迫切性，批評建制派為「乘人之危」急於修改《議事規則》，凌駕幼童的需要。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】【修議規戰】逾300市民立會外集會抗議 戴耀廷指中共「威權管治」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【人大選舉】獲入閘成候選人 劉夢熊：平常心看待"},{"pid":"fcbfdbeeb58107832921e067eb63c77265e04693","tid":498308,"uid":124499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/000959_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F000959_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6707e980&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d739b6e366a605407db83dc4045e52c8ed1202","tid":498308,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkk39dBGPAt4&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNsvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=4dd7ff3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4</a>"},{"pid":"f47ead16b1a69dc90a0cecddba5987bc8cd3723c","tid":498308,"uid":135217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T18:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkk39dBGPAt4&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNsvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=4dd7ff3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kk39dBGPAt4</a></blockquote><br />\n當年就係班仆街泛民支持修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}